        public <ELEMENT extends Element,CRITERIA,MATCHER extends CriteriaMatcher<ELEMENT,CRITERIA>> boolean validateByValidatorKind(CriteriaElementValidatorImpl.ValidatorKind validatorKind,
                                                                                                                            MATCHER matcher,
                                                                                                                            ELEMENT element,
                                                                                                                            CRITERIA... criteriaToCheck)
        Function to programmatically call the different validator kinds. Null valued criteria values won't be used for validation.
        Type Parameters:
        ELEMENT - The Element type
        CRITERIA - The criteria type
        MATCHER - The matcher type
        Parameters:
        validatorKind - The validator kind to use
        matcher - The matcher to use
        element - The element to be validated
        criteriaToCheck - the criteria to check
        Returns:
        true, if passed element matches the passed criteria related to the passed validator kind, otherwise false.
